place <br/>for <span class=\"text-blue-600\">Every</span> <span class=\"text-orange-500\">Task</span></h1><p class=\"mt-6 text-slate-500 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-md leading-relaxed\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\">Join a trusted ecosystem where local experts handle your errands, deliveries, and creative needs with professional care.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 sm:gap-4 mt-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition shadow-lg shadow-blue-200 w-full sm:w-auto\" tabindex=\"0\">Post a Task</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"bg-orange-500 text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-orange-600 transition shadow-lg shadow-orange-200 w-full sm:w-auto\" tabindex=\"0\">Complete a Task</button></div></div><div class=\"order-1 md:order-2 relative flex justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"relative w-full max-w-[320px] sm:max-w-[420px] lg:max-w-[480px] aspect-square\"><div class=\"bg-blue-50 rounded-[36px] sm:rounded-[48px] lg:rounded-[60px] w-full h-full grid place-items-center relative overflow-hidden z-0\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center z-10\"><div class=\"bg-orange-400 w-[85%] h-[85%] rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-2xl\"><img alt=\"jomnus\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"50\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"rounded-md w-[90%] h-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fjomnus.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fjomnus.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fjomnus.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75\"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 bg-slate-50/50\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><h2 class=\"text-center text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-12 md:mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">How It Works</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16\"><div class=\"text-center flex flex-col items-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 text-orange-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M8 12h8\"></path><path d=\"M12 8v8\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-slate-900\">1. Post a Task</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[260px]\">Describe what you need help with. Set your budget and deadline.</p></div><div class=\"text-center flex flex-col items-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 text-orange-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21 21-4.34-4.34\"></path><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-slate-900\">2. Choose Your Performer</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[260px]\">Review profiles, ratings, and portfolios of interested performers.</p></div><div class=\"text-center flex flex-col items-center group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 text-orange-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transform group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-300\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-xl mb-3 text-slate-900\">3. Task Done &amp; Verified</h3><p class=\"text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[260px]\">Payment is released only after you approve the completed work.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-20 items-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5 sm:gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-[#FFF4E5] p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-orange-50 transform sm:translate-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check text-orange-500 mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">ID Verification</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\">Built-in identity checks for every single member.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#F0F7FF] p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-blue-50\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star text-blue-500 mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Reputation</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\">Transparent history and community systems.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#F0F7FF] p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-blue-50 transform sm:translate-y-4\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-star text-blue-500 mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.525 2.295a.53.53 0 0 1 .95 0l2.31 4.679a2.123 2.123 0 0 0 1.595 1.16l5.166.756a.53.53 0 0 1 .294.904l-3.736 3.638a2.123 2.123 0 0 0-.611 1.878l.882 5.14a.53.53 0 0 1-.771.56l-4.618-2.428a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-1.973 0L6.396 21.01a.53.53 0 0 1-.77-.56l.881-5.139a2.122 2.122 0 0 0-.611-1.879L2.16 9.795a.53.53 0 0 1 .294-.906l5.165-.755a2.122 2.122 0 0 0 1.597-1.16z\"></path></svg><h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">Reputation</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\">Comprehensive review and community ratings.</p></div><div class=\"bg-[#FFF4E5] p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-orange-50\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-square text-orange-500 mb-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z\"></path></svg><h4 class=\"font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2\">24/7 Support</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\">Personalized dispute resolution services 24/7.</p></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight\">Marketplace Integrity <br/>by Design.</h2><p class=\"text-slate-500 mb-8 leading-relaxed text-base sm:text-lg\">We&#x27;ve built TaskExchange on a foundation of radical transparency. Our &quot;Trusted Curator&quot; model ensures that every interaction is backed by rigorous security protocols and a community-driven reputation engine.</p><div class=\"bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 p-5 rounded-2xl flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"bg-blue-600 text-white p-2 rounded-lg\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700\">Over 1k tasks completed with 99.9% satisfaction rate.</span></div></div></section><section class=\"py-16 sm:py-20 md:py-24 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class